    goals.cold_start_analysis  

    • Uses of CompareWarmStartToColdBase in goals.cold_start_analysis

      Subclasses of CompareWarmStartToColdBase in goals.cold_start_analysis 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  MAIN_CompareWarmStartToColdEveryStep
      This version runs a normal sequence of game.actions, but adds another cold-started runner at every timestep, and seeing the distance travelled before failure for each.
      class  MAIN_CompareWarmStartToColdMulti
      Take a known sequence of reasonable game.actions, and introduce extra runners all along the way with the same state, but lacking the warm-start of the physics engine solver.
      class  MAIN_CompareWarmStartToColdSingle
      Take a known sequence of reasonable game.actions, simulate for some number of game.actions, and introduce a second runner, with a cloned state, but a cold start of the Box2D internal solvers.
